## Block Entity

---



[Block Condition Type](https://origins.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/block_condition_types/block_entity)

Checks if the block has a block entity.

Type ID: `origins:block_entity`




---

### Examples

```json
"block_condition": {
    "type": "origins:block_entity"
}
```
